data.description: SELLER WILL PAY $5K TOWARDS SELLER CONCESSIONS! Welcome Home! Location, Location, Location!!! This gem is located walking distance to the Decatur Square! This open concept home is complete with 3 large bedrooms, an adorable kitchen with granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, painted cabinets, engineered woodflooring and a completely updated bathroom! The driveway is a pass through from Walnut St to Main Street. Park your lawn chairs in the front yard for front row to all the Decatur Parades! Zoned Commercial and Residential! Check with city for more information.
